{"tid":2325284,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國外交部：請北京當局立即停止針對黎智英","createTime":"2020-12-14T12:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T13:31:32.000Z","uid":53844,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0454fc8ea48ef70799456d626241a7198a8547ae","tid":2325284,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒創辦人黎智英遭加控涉及港版國安法的「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全」罪名，英國外交部開腔，要求港府停止針對黎智英。<br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文（Dominic Raab）發表聲明指：「香港國安法違反具有國際約束力的《聯合聲明》，而現在被用來起訴黎智英，這突顯當局繼續打擊人民的權利和自由，我們已經向香港當局提及此案，並呼籲他們結束針對黎氏和其他親民主的聲音。」"},{"pid":"e85c5a42c88e6b5a7c4d9ef4aa359f94257cb567","tid":2325284,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:43:43.000Z","msg":"再低聲下氣D"},{"pid":"c71349d44c2264dae9eca108613b454f6adc2b82","tid":2325284,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb91a381a43e086f5c016b688e13bb4f6905e5d","tid":2325284,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"又口交了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79beb864a673c3ae827068447d97755f64b3ff7c","tid":2325284,"uid":8776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:46:16.000Z","msg":"請<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81d752eee2890c2ca713ef47718e3314656e867","tid":2325284,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T12:46:44.000Z","msg":"制裁咗未<br />\n流浮山刀手都到咗"},{"pid":"4681c344a429f9db730e44f7b3331a6221